<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="803" height="480" viewBox="0 0 803 480"><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="white"/><rect x="28" y="24" width="120" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="88" y="45" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13" fill="#111111">A</text><rect x="188" y="24" width="120" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="248" y="45" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13" fill="#111111">B</text><line x1="88" y1="56" x2="88" y2="424" stroke="#555" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="6 4"/><line x1="248" y1="56" x2="248" y2="424" stroke="#555" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="6 4"/><rect x="24" y="200" width="730" height="56" rx="2" ry="2" fill="#eef6ff" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><polygon points="24,200 56,200 56,214 50,220 24,220" fill="#eef6ff" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><text x="30" y="214" font-family="monospace" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="#111">ref</text><text x="32" y="232" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">External dependency handshake with a very long descriptive line that previously escaped the ref block.</text><text x="32" y="248" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">Return payload includes another long descriptive line to stress multiline measurement.</text><rect x="28" y="280" width="751" height="120" rx="2" ry="2" fill="#fafafa" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><polygon points="28,280 775,280 775,294 769,300 28,300" fill="#fafafa" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><text x="36" y="294" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" font-weight="600" fill="#111">group This group label is intentionally verbose so the container width follows measured content correctly</text><line x1="88" y1="88" x2="248" y2="88" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="248,88 240,83 240,93" fill="#111" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="96" y="80" text-anchor="start" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">kickoff</text><line x1="88" y1="328" x2="248" y2="328" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="248,328 240,323 240,333" fill="#111" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="96" y="320" text-anchor="start" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">work</text><path d="M28,120 H717 L731 134 V168 H28 Z" fill="#fff8c4" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><path d="M717 120 V134 H731" fill="none" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="36" y="140" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">This is a very long yellow note line that should force the container to grow wider than defaults.</text><text x="36" y="156" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">And this second line keeps the multiline height constraints honest.</text><rect x="28" y="424" width="120" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="88" y="445" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13" fill="#111111">A</text><rect x="188" y="424" width="120" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="248" y="445" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13" fill="#111111">B</text></svg>
